    <description>Nimo-Ilhan Ahmed Ali is a doctoral researcher at the School of Oriental and African Studies, University of London. Her PhD research examined the expansion of higher education sector in Somaliland. She has been involved in the initial planning of the Somaliland National Employment Strategy.
